                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        (298,	1,	'2022-08-28 10:46:11',	'2022-08-28 10:46:11',	'<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>The standard Lorem Ipsum passage, used since the 1500s</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\"The truth is that pain itself is important, it is followed by education, but it happens at such a time that there is some great work and pain. For I will come to the bottom of it, no one should practice any kind of work unless he derives some advantage from it. he wants to be a hair of pain, let him run away from joy, and no one will give birth. Unless they are blinded by desire, they do not come out, they are in fault who abandon their duties, and the soul softens, that is toils.\"</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Section 1.10.32 of \"On the Limits of Good and Evil\", written by Cicero in 45 BC</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\"But in order that you may see whence comes all this born error of those who accuse pleasure and praise pain, I will open the whole matter, and I will explain the very things which were said by that discoverer of truth and, as it were, the architect of a happy life. great sorrows result to those who do not know how to pursue pleasure with reason. Nor is there anyone who loves pain because it is pain, pursues it, wants to gain it, but because such times never occur when he seeks some great pleasure through labor and pain. For I will come to the smallest , who of us undertakes any laborious exercise of the body, except in order that some benefit may result from it?or he who shuns pain, that in which no pleasure is born?\"</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->',	'Is Haaland the \'final piece\' in Man City jigsaw?',	'',	'publish',	'open',	'open',	'',	'is-haaland-the-final-piece-in-man-city-jigsaw',	'',	'',	'2022-08-28 10:46:11',	'2022-08-28 10:46:11',	'',	0,	'http://localhost/blaze-main/local-news-pro/?p=298',	0,	'post',	'',	0),
